{"title":"Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #17: Enve Melee","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-enve-melee","date":1742408051000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-enve-melee\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #17: Enve Melee</a></p>\n\n<p>Whether you’re on the lookout for a new bike or just want to try out some of the world’s best, <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">Cyclist Track Days</a> offer a unique experience to test the latest top-end bikes from the leading brands on the market. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next up in our run-through of some of the incredible bikes that you can test ride at this years Track Days is the Enve Melee.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Melee is Enve’s all-round race bike that is ridden by ProTeam TotalEnergies. It was the Utah brand’s first stock bike and based on its first frameset, the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/enve-launches-its-first-complete-road-bike-the-custom-road\">Custom Road</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tech editor Sam Challis reviewed the Melee in 2023 and said it was ‘one of the best bikes in its class with a touch of extra practicality’. He praised the bike’s lively ride feel, well-designed integration, high perceived build quality and practical extra features. He rode a build with everything Enve outside of the Shimano Dura-Ace Di2 groupset and Sella Italia saddle, and that weighed in at 7.2kg for a 56cm. The Melee is priced at £5,500 for the frameset.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Read Sam’s full Enve Melee review <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/enve-melee-review\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Enve Melee will be at the following Track Days events:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>26<sup>th</sup> April 2025, Odd Down Cycle Track Bath,<br />17<sup>th</sup> May 2025, Lee Valley VeloPark London,<br />7<sup>th</sup> June 2025, The Brownlee Centre, Leeds</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For more information on Cyclist Track Days click <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/cc/cyclist-track-days-2025-3855053\" target=\"_blank\">BOOK YOUR TICKET HERE</a></strong></h3>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-basso-sv\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #14: Basso SV</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-trek-madone-slr\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #5: Trek Madone SLR</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-van-rysel-rcr\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #1: Van Rysel RCR</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 info and how to get tickets</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\